{"title":"Ride Bikes & Bring Stuff with Ortlieb’s Smart New ’25 Line of Products","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ortlieb-new-2025-line-of-products/","date":1725994093000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Pack-Flex-mounting-area-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" alt=\"(Photos / Ron Frazelle)\" /></p>\n<p>While attending the MADE Show a few weeks ago, I got to catch up with Ortlieb and chat about their innovative new products. Since 1982, the German brand has been known for its innovative and weatherproof bags for both on and off the bike. This new run of gear is no exception.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s quite a bit to cover, so let’s dive right in!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The 2025 Ortlieb Gear</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Cack-side-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Cack-side-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Dry Cack side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Cack-side-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Cack-side-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Cack-side-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Cack-side-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Ron Frazelle)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-cord-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-cord-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags dry-pack elastic cord\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-cord-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-cord-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-cord-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-cord-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-removal-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-removal-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags dry pack elastic removal\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-removal-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-removal-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-removal-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dry-pack-elastic-removal-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Dry-Pack</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $65 (12L), $75 (16L)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Ortlieb Dry-Pack is a rear-specific, multifunctional dry bag that is waterproof. It has dual roll closures on either end for quick access. A clever valve is included to get the air out while you compress the bag. The 12L version weighs in at 230g and the 16L comes in at 250L. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The O-Straps Rack helps to ensure a secure and wobble-free fit. Built-in daisy chains offer flexible positioning. Sustainably made in Germany with PU-coated nylon fabric, this bag is ready to work! </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Duffle Lite</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duffle_Lite_K1438_front-LargeNew-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Duffle-lite-jpeg-e1725920866577.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"665\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duffle_Lite_K1438_front-LargeNew-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Duffle-lite-jpeg-e1725920866577.webp\" alt=\"Duffle_Lite_K1438_front LargeNew 2025 Ortlieb Bags Duffle lite\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duffle_Lite_K1438_front-LargeNew-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Duffle-lite-jpeg-e1725920866577.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duffle_Lite_K1438_front-LargeNew-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Duffle-lite-jpeg-e1725920866577-297x154.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duffle_Lite_K1438_front-LargeNew-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Duffle-lite-jpeg-e1725920866577-120x62.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Duffle_Lite_K1438_front-LargeNew-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Duffle-lite-jpeg-e1725920866577-768x399.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $230 (40L), $250 (60L)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ortlieb’s new Duffle Lite might be the bag you need for trekking, loading in cycling gear, paddle sports, or just traveling the globe. It comes in two sizes, the 40L which weighs in at 760g. Or, the 60L size, weighing in at 850g. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has a cool waterproof TIZIP zipper that offers IP67 protection and comes with a removable inner pocket. Sustainably made in Germany with PU-coated nylon fabric, this duffle is ready to travel with durability and functionality! </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Handlebar-Pack Flex</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Pack-front-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Pack-front-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Dry-Pack front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Pack-front-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Pack-front-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Pack-front-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Dry-Pack-front-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Pack-Flex-mounting-area-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Pack-Flex-mounting-area-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Handlebar-Pack Flex mounting area\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Pack-Flex-mounting-area-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Pack-Flex-mounting-area-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Pack-Flex-mounting-area-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Pack-Flex-mounting-area-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Ron Frazelle)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dryHandlebar-Pack-Flex-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dryHandlebar-Pack-Flex-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags dryHandlebar Pack Flex\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dryHandlebar-Pack-Flex-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dryHandlebar-Pack-Flex-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dryHandlebar-Pack-Flex-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-dryHandlebar-Pack-Flex-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $145 (15L)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With its multiple mounting options, this new 25L bikepacking bag would be ideal for carrying your sleeping gear. It is 100% waterproof and mounts to the handlebar with any Ortlieb Mounting set (sold separately). The roll closures on both sides make for easy access. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the attachment of additional equipment, there is an elastic drawstring and hooks to secure stuff to the bag. There is a valve to help let the air out during compression, allowing the bag to get smaller, tighter, and more secure. The new Handlebar-Pack Flex has a load capacity of five kilos.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Handlebar-Rack</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-rack-tall-jpeg-e1725921006874.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"780\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-rack-tall-jpeg-e1725921006874.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Handlebar rack tall\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-rack-tall-jpeg-e1725921006874.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-rack-tall-jpeg-e1725921006874-297x181.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-rack-tall-jpeg-e1725921006874-120x73.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-rack-tall-jpeg-e1725921006874-768x468.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-back-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-back-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Handlebar Rack back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-back-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-back-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-back-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-back-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-short-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-short-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Handlebar Rack short\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-short-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-short-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-short-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Handlebar-Rack-short-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $60</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Handlebar-Rack is Ortlieb’s first attempt at a luggage rack for handlebars. This rack like the Handlebar Pack Flex, above is ideal for bikepacking, but can also be used on your city bike. It supports up to 5 kilos and offers three mounting options. This helps the Handlebar-Rack fit a plethora of bicycles and handlebars.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Ortlieb Mounting set (not included) makes installation quick. there are also adjustable rack straps that ensure your load is secure. It’s made of aluminum and ready to help transport your groceries home, or your camping gear to the campsite. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Quick-Rack</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Quick-Rack-side-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Quick-Rack-side-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Quick-Rack side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Quick-Rack-side-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Quick-Rack-side-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Quick-Rack-side-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Quick-Rack-side-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/IMG_4943-Large-2-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/IMG_4943-Large-2-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/IMG_4943-Large-2-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/IMG_4943-Large-2-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/IMG_4943-Large-2-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/IMG_4943-Large-2-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $130 (L), $140 (XL)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Again, Ortlieb delivers another quickly installed, versatile rack in the Quick Rack. It comes in two distinct sizes, large and x-large. This rack is super versatile and comes with secondary attachment levels. This allows for the simultaneous use of side panniers and a basket. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Fitting tires up to 29″ x 3.0″, the XL version of the rack can support up to 27kg. The L version supports up to 20kg and 28″ x 2″ tires. The cool thing about this rack system is the ability to install it in a claimed 15 seconds and remove it in 5. Making it easy to switch from bike to bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both racks are also compatible with the new Thru Axle M6-Connector, QL 3.1, and of course all of their bag attachments, QL2.1, QL3.1, etc</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Sling-Bag Metroshpere</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-closures-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-closures-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Metrosphere closures\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-closures-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-closures-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-closures-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-closures-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-back-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-back-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Metrosphere back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-back-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-back-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-back-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Metrosphere-back-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $80 (8L)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern design highlights meet functionality with the new Ortlieb Metrosphere Sling Bag. The reinforced roll closure with its self-locking magnets allows whatever you have stored in the 3L sling to stay secure. It’s waterproof, sustainably made, and the perfect everyday companion for all of your essentials. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Thru-Axle M6 Connector</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-rear-Thru-Axcle-M6-Connector-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-rear-Thru-Axcle-M6-Connector-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags rear Thru Axcle M6 Connector\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-rear-Thru-Axcle-M6-Connector-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-rear-Thru-Axcle-M6-Connector-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-rear-Thru-Axcle-M6-Connector-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-rear-Thru-Axcle-M6-Connector-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Rear-thru-Axle-M6-Connector-in-action-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Rear-thru-Axle-M6-Connector-in-action-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Rear thru Axle M6 Connector in action\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Rear-thru-Axle-M6-Connector-in-action-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Rear-thru-Axle-M6-Connector-in-action-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Rear-thru-Axle-M6-Connector-in-action-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Rear-thru-Axle-M6-Connector-in-action-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $40</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a universal thru-axle that is used for mounting the Ortlieb Quick-Rack line. It uses an adjustable length range of 165/168mm, all the way up to 180mm. So the Thru-Axle M6-Connector can be used for all sorts of bikes. On both ends, you’ll find M6 threaded mounts which allow for the use of panniers o trailers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Thru Axle is made of high-quality aluminum in Germany and comes in three thread pitches; 1, 1.5, and 1.75mm. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Velo-Sling</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-front-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-front-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Velo Sling front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-front-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-front-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-front-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-front-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-magnet-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-magnet-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Velo Sling magnet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-magnet-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-magnet-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-magnet-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-magnet-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-mounting-area-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-mounting-area-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"New 2025 Ortlieb Bags Velo Sling mounting area\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-mounting-area-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-mounting-area-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-mounting-area-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/New-2025-Ortlieb-Bags-Velo-Sling-mounting-area-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $95 (3L)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Ortlieb Velo-Sling is a waterproof handlebar bag hybrid that allows you to use it as both a handlebar bag and an off-the-bike sling. As a handlebar bag, it’s versatile for bikepacking, MTB, or city adventures. The Velo-Sling uses a roll closure and magnets to keep it fastened. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It also offers 3L of waterproof storage and can fit things like your wallet, phone, and jacket. Sporting an inner zipper compartment, it helps you get organized. The O-straps and rubber cord keep it rattle-free while attached to the bars. Use the compression straps to further secure the load. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Use the detachable shoulder strap to carry it around town with you. it’s also sustainably made in Germany and comes in Ortlieb’s bikepacking colors,  black or sand.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.ortlieb.com/usa_en/\">Ortlieb.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ortlieb-new-2025-line-of-products/\">Ride Bikes &amp; Bring Stuff with Ortlieb’s Smart New ’25 Line of Products</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"94aeb86c55f69e4ad191c1f2d770d35b827533f8219d546d275a5881d6317d39","category":"Cycling"}